v class=""><div class="aa8f50 e1833d"><div class="b0b19c"><span class="b04b30 d63583">New Arrival</span></div><p class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 b493f8">Relaxed-fit T-shirt in lightweight jersey with a casual but not oversized silhouette. Ribbed crew neck, dropped shoulders, and a straight-cut hem. Made with COOLMAX® fiber – an engineered channelled fiber that wicks moisture away from the body to the fabric surface.</p><p class="b04b30 f55cde" data-testid="description-article-number">Art. No.:<!-- --> <!-- -->1328845004</p><dl class="a4c5da"><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Concept: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7" data-testid="description-concepts">BASICS</dd></div><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Description: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7" data-testid="description-detailedDescriptions">Teal, Solid colour</dd></div><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Length: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7" data-testid="description-garmentLength">Regular length</dd></div><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Sleeve Length: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7" data-testid="description-sleeveLength">Short sleeve</dd></div><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Fit: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7" data-testid="description-fits">Relaxed fit</dd></div><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Neckline: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7" data-testid="description-neckLineStyle">Round neck</dd></div><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Functions: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7" data-testid="description-functionality">Moisture-wicking</dd></div><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Quantity: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7" data-testid="description-quantitySalesMode">N/A</dd></div></dl></div></div></div></div><div class="dafb45"><button type="button" class="a2e9ad b34f1f edb270" aria-expanded="false" aria-disabled="false" id="toggle-materialsAndSuppliersAccordion" aria-controls="section-materialsAndSuppliersAccordion"><span class="f96cb6">Materials</span><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="16" width="16" class="e3009e"><path d="M8.75 7.25V0h-1.5v7.25H0v1.5h7.25V16h1.5V8.75H16v-1.5H8.75Z"></path></svg></button><div id="section-materialsAndSuppliersAccordion" aria-labelledby="toggle-materialsAndSuppliersAccordion" aria-hidden="true" hidden="" class="f88a58 e57e56" role="region" style="display: none; height: 0px; opacity: 0;"><div class=""><div class="aa8f50 e1833d"><div class="b103ee"><h3 class="b9e19c b1dbab c3f7b3">Composition</h3><ul class="b2b6a8"><li class="b819ff"><span class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 d20aac">Cotton 54%, Polyester 46%</span></li></ul></div><dl class="b103ee"><div class="e36ab4"><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd e3e2e8">Material: </dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 a667b7">Jersey</dd></div></dl><section class="b103ee"><h3 class="b9e19c b1dbab c3f7b3">Materials in this product explained</h3><dl><div><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd f32842">Cotton</dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 d9737e">Cotton is a soft and versatile natural fibre harvested from the cotton plant.</dd></div><div><dt class="fdb3e1 a2d4fd f32842">Polyester</dt><dd class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 d9737e">Polyester is a synthetic fibre made from crude oil (a fossil resource).</dd></div></dl></section></div></div></div></div><div class="dafb45"><button type="button" class="a2e9ad b34f1f edb270" aria-expanded="false" aria-disabled="false" id="toggle-deliveryAndPaymentAccordion" aria-controls="section-deliveryAndPaymentAccordion"><span class="f96cb6">Delivery and Payment</span><svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="16" width="16" class="e3009e"><path d="M8.75 7.25V0h-1.5v7.25H0v1.5h7.25V16h1.5V8.75H16v-1.5H8.75Z"></path></svg></button><div id="section-deliveryAndPaymentAccordion" aria-labelledby="toggle-deliveryAndPaymentAccordion" aria-hidden="true" hidden="" class="f88a58 e57e56" role="region" style="display: none; height: 0px; opacity: 0;"><div class=""><div class="aa8f50 e1833d"><div><p class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 ca6d2d">Delivery in 6-12 business days</p><p class="fdb3e1 cfeb83 ca6d2d">Free delivery on all orders over PHP 2,499. For orders below, PHP 2,499, a shipping fee of PHP 149 will be applied. ​ Your parcel will be delivered to your home or an alternate address within the following business days: NCR: 6-8 days, Luzon: 8-10 days, Visayas:9-10 days, Mindanao: 10-12 days. At the moment, all orders are shipping out from our warehouse in Malaysia. Occasionally, you may experience a longer delivery lead time, especially during sales periods. PAYMENT: We accept MasterCard, Visa credit cards and cash on delivery. Learn more on our customer service pages.​</p><p class="beae19 ca6d2d" data-testid="customer-service-information">For more information, please visit our Customer Service pages for <a class="d810bb def1f3" href="https://www2.hm.com/en_ph/customer-service/delivery.html" aria-label="Delivery information">Delivery</a>, <a class="d810bb def1f3" href="https://www2.hm.com/en_ph/customer-service/payments-info.html" aria-label="Payment information">Payments</a> and <a class="d810bb def1f3" href="https://www2.hm.com/en_ph/customer-service/returns.html" aria-label="Return information">Returns</a>.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="e0bbeb f83365 f0e4eb"></div><div class="__9HO5"><div><section id="pdp_pra_style_with" class="PvgI" aria-labelledby="style-with-id"><div role="presentation" aria-roledescription="carousel" class="c0beb0" data-testid="reco"><div class="d9d1fa"><div class="c41969"><h2 class="b9e19c b1dbab c171fc cb3f46" id="style-with-id">Style with</h2></div><div class="db2fdb"><button class="cb1046 c7e5ac c4feb2 ac834b ed2d40" disabled="" aria-disabled="true" type="button"><span class="ad8938"><svg role="img" aria-hidden=