ent chapters. Depending on if you are a subscriber, member or if you have an H\u0026M Account, different parts of the notice will apply to you. In each chapter, we describe in more detail what personal data we have about you and how we use it. We have also increased the information on your rights, for example how to get access to your data and how you can request to terminate the usage of your data.","linkText":"You can find our Privacy Notice here","buttonText":"Ok"},"luminaires":{"regulationText":"Regulation (EU) No: 874/2012","energyLabelling":"Energy rating","compatible":"This luminaire is compatible with bulbs of energy classes:","energyDeclaration":"Energy rating","imageNumber":"874/2012"},"turnTo":{"labels":{"reviewesLabel":"Reviews","finishReview":"Finish this review","submitReviewCTA":"Send my review","helpHeading":"Help us rate your latest purchase","greeting":"Hi","shareExperienceCta":"Share your experience","shareExperienceCtaText":"and help others make great decisions, please rate your latest purchase","productSatHeading":"Product satisfaction","productSatText":"Rate your product satisfaction","ratingHeading":"Rating","sizeFitHeading":"Size and fit","myProfileHeading":"My profile","myProfileText":"Help others make great decisions, tell them a little about yourself.","reviewTextLong":"What do you think? People talk about quality, look and feel.","thankYouHeading":"Thank you!","thankYouText":"Your feedback is much appreciated","moreReviewCta":"Your reviews are really valuable","moreReviewCta2":"Let's go for another one!","othersLabel":"What other customers think based on","numberReviews":"{xx} reviews","numberReviewsMenu":"Reviews ({xx})","numberComments":"{xx} comments","othersHeading":"WHAT OTHER CUSTOMERS THINK","userProfileShort":"in size {size}","commentTitle":"Comment","commentText":"What do you think? People talk about quality, look and feel.","basedText":"Based on","customerReviews":"customer reviews","basedOnCustomerReviews":"[basedOnCustomerRevi