ity","beautyArea":"Beauty area","homewareStyle":"Homeware style","sustainablySourcedMaterials":"Additional material information","material":"Material","productSize":"Product size","woodCompositions":"Wood type","woodCompositionsCountries":"Origin of wood","yearOfProduction":"Year of production","shrinkageInfo":"Information on shrinkage","sizestandardReference":"Reference to Size standard","nameOfImporter":"Imported by","botanicalName":"Botanical name","quantitySalesMode":"Quantity","lightNeeds":"Light needs","wateringNeeds":"Watering needs","careAndMaintenanceInstructions":"Care and maintenance instructions","plantAndFlowerStyle":"Plant and flower style","plantHeight":"Plant height (including inner pot)","disclaimerFlowersPlants":"Disclaimer","plantType":"Plant type","temperature":"Temperature","recommendedAge":"Recommended age","seats":"Number of seats","stuffingMaterial":"Stuffing material","firmness":"Firmness","manufacturingLicenseNumber":"[manufacturingLicenseNumber]","usedByDate":"[usedByDate]","batchNumber":"[batchNumber]"},"accordionLabels":{"description":"Description","descriptionAndFit":"Description \u0026 fit","descriptionAndSize":"Description \u0026 size","materialComposition":"Materials \u0026 suppliers","careGuide":"Care guide","additionalInformation":"Additional information","supplierInformation":"Supplier information","materials":"Materials","howToUse":"How to use"},"higg":{"heading":"Materials environmental impact","descriptions":["The materials in this product show less than a 12.5% reduction across four key environmental impacts, when compared to conventional materials (for example, organic cotton compared to regular cotton).","The materials in this product show at least a 12.5% reduction across four key environmental impacts, when compared to conventional materials (for example, organic cotton compared to regular cotton).","The materials in this product show at least a 25% reduction across four key environmental impacts, when compared to conventional materials (for example, organic cotton compared to regular cotton).","The materials in this product show at least a 50% reduction across four key environmental impacts, when compared to conventional materials (for example, organic cotton compared to regular cotton)."],"levelAchievementLabels":["Baseline","Level 1","Level 2","Level 3"],"breakdownHeading":"Environmental Impact","breakdownLabels":{"waterUse":"less water use","co2":"less global warming potential","chemicals":"Chemicals","waterPollution":"less water pollution","fossil":"less fossil fuels use"},"breakdownDescription":"The materials in this product show the following reductions in impact when compared to conventional versions of the same materials (for example, a recycled material compared to its virgin version).","breakdownMaterialDescription":"{0} less than conventional materials","disclaimer":{"description":"The Higg Index was developed by the Sustainable Apparel Coalition, a global multi-stakeholder nonprofit organization. At H\u0026M, we use the Higg Index to measure and report on the sustainability of product materials.","linkText":"Read more about the Higg Index."},"claim":"Click here for full data and methodology information","explanatoryText":"These ratings are based on the environmental impact of a product’s materials, which represent the majority of a garment’s total impact. The calculated reductions presented here do not reflect regional variations but are a representative of global average impacts."},"kcNumbers":{"title":"KC-number","description":"[Children's Product Certification] As a safety check item, the following national integrated certification is required","confirmationNumber":"Safety confirmation report number"},"sizeRecoForNewCustomer":{"recommendedSizeText":"Recommended size: {0}","findMySizeBodyText":"Please provide the following details","height":"Height","weight":"Weight","age":"Age","heightUnit":"cm","weightUnit":"kg","ageUnit":"years","sizeRecommendation":"Size recommenda